title: TorrentRatioKeeper Monster (Classic Edition) v3.0
description:
Release of TRK v3.0 (ratio/upload increase tool for all private trackers).
* Support for uTorrent/BitTorrent/BitComet/Vuse/ABC/BitLord torrent clients.
* Support for https trackers for uTorrent/BitComet.
* Classic Skin.

Expert features:
1. No download reports anymore, just uploading! Tracker will see you as seeder. :)
2. No uploading reports. You can use it with first feature to emulate "network problems". On tracker's stats you will not upload/download at all.

To works with vista/windows 7 (32/64bits) need to lunch TRK and Torrent client as Admin:
Right click on icon and click "Run as Administrator".
